.Dd December 27, 2017
.Dt RPC.SPRAYD 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm rpc.sprayd ,
.Nm sprayd
.Nd spray server
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm /usr/libexec/rpc.sprayd
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility
is a server which records packets sent by the
.Xr spray 8
command and sends a traffic report to the originator of the packets.
The
.Nm
daemon is normally invoked by
.Xr inetd 8 .
.Pp
The
.Nm
utility uses an
.Tn RPC
protocol defined in
.Pa /usr/include/rpcsvc/spray.x .
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr spray 8
